kpi_info.title: period_duration
kpi_info.use: Duration of the measurement period in minutes.

kpi_info.title: ET_TOTAL_ERROR_CODE
kpi_info.use: Error code concerning the whole report. Zerovalue means a successful report, nonzero value indicates that no counters are present. The value is a general DX error code in decimal format.

kpi_info.title: ET_DIST_ERROR_CODE
kpi_info.use: Error code concerning the short disturbances counters. Zero value means a successful report, nonzero value indicates that no disturbance counters are present. The value is a general DX error code in decimal format.

kpi_info.title: ET_FRA_ERROR_CODE
kpi_info.use: Error code concerning the frame alignment error counters. Zero value means a successful report, nonzero value indicates that no frame alignment counters are present. The value is a general DX error code in decimal format.

kpi_info.title: ET_SLIP_ERROR_CODE
kpi_info.use: Error code concerning the slip counters. Zerovalue means a successful report, nonzero value indicates that no slip counters are present. The value is a general DX error code in decimal format.

kpi_info.title: ET_CRC_ERROR_CODE
kpi_info.use: Error code concerning the CRC counters. Zero value means a successful report, nonzero value indicates that no CRC counters are present. The value is a general DX error code in decimal format.
